room_title: Escape room "The Hostel" by Escape at the Shore in Atlantic City
room_description: During your trip to Europe, one of your friends goes missing after an adventure at the local hostel. He's been kidnapped by a black market circle that specializes in human trafficking and torture. You decide to save him yourselves but walk right into the kidnappers' trap. The whole group has been cuffed to opposite walls inside a torture chamber and Barry has been strapped to an electric chair! Can you escape your gruesome fate?
